-- New Zealand Rugby Union Appoints Steve Hansen as Head Coach of All Blacks
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2011-12-16T02:14:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/new-zealand-rugby-union-appoints-steve-hansen-as-head-coach-of-all-blacks.html
The New Zealand Rugby Union said it
appointed Steve Hansen to replace  Graham Henry  as coach of the
world champion All Blacks team on a two-year contract.  Hansen was the only candidate recommended by an
appointments panel to be interviewed by the full NZRU Board, the
Wellington-based governing body said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  